{
  "texts": [
    "In Supplementary Fig. 6, we present the identified KIFs for TCGA-BRCA and TCGA-OV with their frequencies as top 10 most contributing factors of latent features.",
    "For TCGA-BRCA dataset, the identified KIFs included 11 genes, all of which were found to be associated with breast cancer in existing studies (see Supplementary Table 5 for more details).",
    "For example, the study 29 found that CDC20 knockdown inhibited the migration of metastatic MDA-MB-231 breast cancer cell line.",
    "Recent studies also demonstrated that FABP4 promotes obesityassociated breast cancer development 30.",
    "For PSMB9, the study 31 found that PSMB9 was overexpressed in breast cancer cells."
  ]
}